name: Abdule kalam
caption: अगर तुम सूरज की तरह चमकना चाहते हो, तो सूरज की तरह जलना सीखो।
author: डॉ. एपीजे अब्दुल कलाम

name: Larry Page
caption: Sun sets in the West, the smile on the face is the best.

name: Larry Page
caption: If you’re changing the world, you’re working on important things. You’re excited to get up in the morning.
author: Larry Page

name: Oscar Wilde
caption: Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.
author: Oscar Wilde

name: Aristotle
caption: It is during our darkest moments that we must focus to see the light.
author: Aristotle

name: Helen Keller
caption: The best and most beautiful things in the world cannot be seen or even touched - they must be felt with the heart.
author: Helen Keller

name: Benjamin Franklin
caption: Well done is better than well said.
author: Benjamin Franklin

name: Eleanor Roosevelt
caption: Do one thing every day that scares you.
author: Eleanor Roosevelt

name: Martin Luther King Jr.
caption: Darkness cannot drive out darkness: only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate: only love can do that.
author: Martin Luther King Jr.

name: Franklin D. Roosevelt
caption: The only thing we have to fear is fear itself.
author: Franklin D. Roosevelt

name: Mother Teresa
caption: Spread love everywhere you go. Let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.
author: Mother Teresa

name: Mahatma Gandhi
caption: You must be the change you wish to see in the world.
author: Mahatma Gandhi

name: John Lennon
caption: You may say I'm a dreamer, but I'm not the only one. I hope someday you'll join us. And the world will live as one.
author: John Lennon

name: James Cameron
caption: If you set your goals ridiculously high and it's a failure, you will fail above everyone else's success.
author: James Cameron

name: River
caption: If you look at what you have in life, you'll always have more. If you look at what you don't have in life, you'll never have enough.
author: Oprah Winfrey

name: City
caption: The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.
author: Eleanor Roosevelt

name: Apple
caption: Your time is limited, so don't waste it living someone else's life. Don't be trapped by dogma – which is living with the results of other people's thinking.
author: Steve Jobs

name: land
caption: The greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall .
author: Nelson Mandela

name: Red
caption: The way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing .
author: Walt Disney
